      <title>Updated Apple Developer Program License Agreement now available</title>
      <link>https://n-kase.github.io/rss/posts/post-526/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 19:15:09 +0900</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://n-kase.github.io/rss/posts/post-526/</guid>
      <description>&lt;![CDATA[<h2 id="aiによる要約">AIによる要約
</h2><p>Appleは2024年12月6日にApple Developer Programライセンス契約の添付ファイル2を改訂し、In-App Purchase APIの利用要件を明確にしたため、開発者は変更内容を確認しアカウントで更新後の利用規約に同意する必要があり、これによりアプリの収益化方法やプラットフォームポリシーへの適合が見直され、開発者コミュニティでの議論が活発になることが予想されるため、開発者は速やかに改訂版を確認し自分のアプリが要件に合致しているかを検証し、同意手続きを完了させるべきである。</p>
<h2 id="和訳本文">和訳本文
</h2><h2 id="updated-apple-developer-program-license-agreement-now-available">Updated Apple Developer Program License Agreement now available
</h2><p>December 6, 2024</p>
<p>Attachment 2 of the Apple Developer Program License Agreement has been amended to specify requirements for use of the In-App Purchase API. Please review the changes and accept the updated terms in your account.</p>
<p><a class="link" href="https://developer.apple.com/support/terms/apple-developer-program-license-agreement/"  target="_blank" rel="noopener"
    >View the full terms and conditions</a></p>
<p>Translations of the updated agreement will be available on the <a class="link" href="https://developer.apple.com/support/terms/"  target="_blank" rel="noopener"
    >Apple Developer website</a> within one month.</p>
<hr>
<h2 id="元スレッド記事本文">元スレッド・記事本文
</h2><h2 id="updated-apple-developer-program-license-agreement-now-available-1">Updated Apple Developer Program License Agreement now available
</h2><p>December 6, 2024</p>
<p>Attachment 2 of the Apple Developer Program License Agreement has been amended to specify requirements for use of the In-App Purchase API. Please review the changes and accept the updated terms in your account.</p>
<p><a class="link" href="https://developer.apple.com/support/terms/apple-developer-program-license-agreement/"  target="_blank" rel="noopener"
    >View the full terms and conditions</a></p>
<p>Translations of the updated agreement will be available on the <a class="link" href="https://developer.apple.com/support/terms/"  target="_blank" rel="noopener"
    >Apple Developer website</a> within one month.</p>
]]></description>
